    Exercise       Argument                    figure             input file

    exhpc_1     bit manipulation routines

  exhpc_2       Morton order                  plkey_M.ps

 exhpc_3        Hilbert key                   plkey_H.ps


  exhpc_4         Quadtree                     pltree.ps        tree.dat

  exhpc_5         KD -tree                     plkdtree.ps


 
These  ancillary routines are used in some exercises:

- sorti     : sort an integer array 
- whenigt  : find elements of an array greater than 
- selecti  : partition M(<=N) elements  of an array of size N . Cf. Numerical 
             Recipes II ed. , Section 8.5

The fortran version of these routines is available upon request 



